text: Interesting. NSA Director Adm. Mike Rogers just said arguing about encryption is pointless: "So spending time arguing about ‘hey, encryption is bad and we ought to do away with it’ … that’s a waste of time to me”

attachments.title: NSA Chief Stakes Out Pro-Encryption Position, in Contrast to FBI
attachments.text: Mike Rogers said Thursday that “encryption is foundational to the future,” and arguing about it is a waste of time.
